# ── Official rating sheets (plan.md §20)
# "Rubric IP: official rating sheets are the orgs' IP... never republish rubric PDFs/text
#  wholesale." These 44 PDFs are FBLA's copyrighted documents. They stay local.
# The app does not need them at runtime — rubrics/catalog.json and the structured
# *.rubric.json files are enough. You only need the PDFs to re-run `npm run parse-rubrics`.
rubrics/*.pdf

# generated by predev/prebuild
public/ffmpeg/
